<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Eshop Activation Email</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      color: #222222;
    }
    a {
      color: #0070f3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: #0070f3;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }

    /* Layout */
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .email-header {
      background: #0070f3;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .email-footer {
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f6f6f6;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Buttons */
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0;
        border-radius: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      Eshop Account Activation
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with <strong>Eshop</strong>! To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>

      <h1><%= otp %></h1>

      <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>
      <p>If you did not register for an Eshop account, please ignore this email.</p>

      <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Activate My Account</a>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please donâ€™t hesitate to contact us at 
        <a href="mailto:support@eshop.com">support@eshop.com</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:10px;">Best regards,<br>The Eshop Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
